name: The I Ching of Blockchain
description:
A collection of carefully selected yet randomly applied words to discover 18³ blockchain tech concepts.

It's simple: Choose your beginning, middle, and end word to create a new idea——an excellent way to sound smart at the next stakeholder meeting or hackathon! 

Inspired by the ancient art of I Ching, may this magic table unlock a hidden path into your decentralized future.

format: PNG
resolution: 5600×5600 
artist: Issey Fujishima
location: Jakarta, Indonesia
